      <bioghist id="aspace_d40b68a077476029aa25a50bbaf0ce00">
         <head>BREWSTER FAMILY</head>
         <p>Elisha Brewster (-1871) m. 1833 Elizabeth Bartlett Bates (1814-1878)</p>
         <p>-----Mary Thomas Brewster (1834-1873) m. 1872 Hon. Henry Long</p>
